      %h2 Parameters
      %p Stick these in as query parameters. e.g. ?count=15&from=1900&to=1910  
      %dl
        %dt count
        %dd The number of returned random DOIs. Max 1000, default 20.
        %dt to
        %dd Only DOIs published before and including year /to/.
        %dt from
        %dd Only DOIs published after and including year /from/.
        %dt issn
        %dd Only journal article DOIs published in a journal with /issn/.
        %dt title
        %dd Only journal article DOIs published in journal with exact full title /title/.
        %dt discipline
        %dd only journal article DOIs published in a journal with discpline category. TODO

      %h2 Randomisation Process
      %p A random distribution of rational values, 0 - 1, has been assigned to our DOI records.

      %h2 Caveats 
      %p 
        DOIs for works published after March 2012 are not available.